Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:20.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:26.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
